(Shut Him Out)

19
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,440
A Cha.

20
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,560
There are few customers tonight
due to bad weather.

21
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,880
Let's close up early.

22
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,200
