23
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,880
A Cha.

24
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,960
Could you open the door for me?

25
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,960
I know you don't want to see me.

26
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,680
But I have something important

27
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,600
to say to you.

28
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:05,880
A Cha, please open the door.

29
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,320
Let me see you.

30
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,480
A Cha.

31
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:11,520
- Why are you here?
- I...

32
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,520
We had a deal.

33
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,040
We are even now.

34
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,840
You are the Young Master,

35
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,080
and I'm a cook.

36
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,600
So what are you doing here?

37
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,040
I'm sorry, I...

38
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,920
Stop.

39
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,400
I don't want you to say anything.

40
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,360
And I don't want to see you.

41
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,920
What are you doing?

42
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,120
Here you are.

43
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,960
I've brought the vegetable

44
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,000
you ordered from the market.

45
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:03,800
In addition,

46
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,720
I'll go and buy fish later.

47
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:07,200
The fish is particularly fresh.

48
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,320
Get out of here.

49
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,680
I know that no matter what,

50
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,840
you won't forgive me.

51
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,640
But I want to prove by my actions

52
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,600
that I said something
that I never meant.

53
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,640
You can hate me

54
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,680
or don't forgive me.

55
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,720
I deserve it.

56
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,960
I am asking you to leave now.

57
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:35,960
Young Master.

58
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:38,600
Are you really going to work here
as a waiter?

59
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,840
Come on.

60
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,280
Think of another way.

61
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,040
Think about how to pursue a girl.

62
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,920
Exactly.

63
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,440
I...

64
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,640
I've never pursued a girl.

65
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,120
That's true.

66
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,200
You were a general at the border.

67
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,720
Now, you're the Young Master.

68
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,080
You're pursued by girls.

69
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,600
I mean,

70
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,400
as the Seventh Young Master,

71
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,360
show us your ability.

72
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,000
My ability?

73
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,800
So you mean

74
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,720
I should perform martial arts for A Cha?

75
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:20,160
Your strength is that you have money.

76
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,880
Money?

77
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,640
One red glazed vase.

78
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,880
One Ruyao blue glazed pot.

79
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,360
One jade Ruyi.

80
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,600
A painting of vigorous pines
by a famous artist.

81
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,000
What are you up to now?

82
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:43,680
A Cha, I got you some gifts.

83
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:44,800
Take them away.

84
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,920
Leave now.

85
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:51,760
You and I have been over.

86
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,560
There's no way to turn back.

87
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:00,080
I don't want to see you buzz around me
like a fly.

88
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,840
I don't want to see you.

89
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,360
Get out of here.

90
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,200
Leave.

91
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:14,360
Fine, I'll leave.

92
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,120
Just don't be angry.

93
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,000
You offended her,

94
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,200
