190
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,600
If you push me away

191
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,120
because of elusive things,

192
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:38,160
and I cut ties with you,

193
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:41,080
