that we're meant to be together.

194
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:42,960
I...

195
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,240
I'm afraid of losing you.

196
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:49,000
What are you afraid of?

197
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,920
My love for you is more

198
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:53,000
than yours for me.

199
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:55,120
I'm willing to stay by your side.

200
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,960
I don't need you to decide for my life.

201
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:01,240
You are depriving me
of the right to like you.

202
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,800
Please

203
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:08,120
